Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.60,0:32:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把我的头发撩到后面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}pulling my hair at the back.<br />
