Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.82,0:33:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}..and to go with him.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.06,0:33:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴维斯太太  你和你朋友们的痛苦经历\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mrs Davies, the ordeal that you and your friends suffered<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.80,0:33:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生在1996年3月6日的晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on the evening of 6th March 1996<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.79,0:33:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是15年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}happened 15 years ago.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.09,0:33:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时是个16岁的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were a girl of 16.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.91,0:33:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.76,0:33:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时很害怕  天也黑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were terrified. It was dark.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.89,0:33:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,综上所诉  你认为你对当时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Given all that, how reliable do you think your memory is<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.71,0:33:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生事件的记忆有多可靠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the events which took place?<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.53,0:33:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对每个细节都记忆犹新\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember every detail like it was yesterday.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.38,0:33:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事不可能忘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't forget something like that.<br />
