Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.19,0:33:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是忘不掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you can't.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.76,0:33:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击你的人摘掉过面罩吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did the man who attacked you ever remove his mask?<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.89,0:33:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.81,0:33:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我确认下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, to be clear...<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.16,0:33:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你或你朋友都没看到过他的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}..at no time did you, or any of your friends, see his face?<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.39,0:34:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.75,0:34:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片中的男子是真正的约翰·库珀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This man in the photograph is the real John Cooper.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.82,0:34:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个和妻子结婚42年的忠诚丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A loving husband who was married to his wife for 42 years.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.81,0:34:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的儿子曾是我们的掌上明珠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had a son who was the apple of our eye.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.53,0:34:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这颗明珠腐坏  伤了他母亲的心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An apple that went bad and broke his mother's heart.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.42,0:34:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我妻子心脏病发而死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe that the heart attack that killed my wife<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.81,0:34:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为她一直以来承受了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was brought on because of the...<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.42,0:34:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压力  悲伤和耻辱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the stress, the sadness and the shame<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.30,0:34:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我明明无辜却遭到牢狱之灾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because of all the time that I spent in prison as an innocent man.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.51,0:34:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方和伊利亚斯先生告诉你们  我是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The police and Mr Elias tell you I'm a liar.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.44,0:34:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说我谎称我大多数衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That I'm lying when I say that most of my clothes,<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.29,0:34:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是我的卡其色泳裤是二手的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}most significantly, my khaki bathers, were second-hand.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.51,0:35:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然  他们无法体会贫穷的滋味\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well... obviously, they don't know what it's like to be poor.<br />
