Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.26,0:35:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家的衣柜里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In my wardrobe at home,<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.62,0:35:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件二手大衣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got an overcoat second-hand<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.17,0:35:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我穿去参加了我妻子的葬礼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I wore to my wife's funeral.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.30,0:35:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪审团的女士们先生们  我为了我没有犯下的罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ladies and gentlemen of the jury, I spent ten years of my life<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.61,0:35:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在牢里待了十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in prison for crimes that I did not commit.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.88,0:35:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要让警方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please... Please, do not allow the police<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.59,0:35:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次让我遭遇不公的审判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to carry out another miscarriage of justice against me.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.55,0:35:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是杀人犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am not a murderer.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.63,0:35:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是强奸犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am not a rapist.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.70,0:35:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个被冤枉的无辜者  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am an innocent man who's been wronged. Thank you.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.18,0:35:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊利亚斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr Elias...<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.13,0:35:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一刻钟到4点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's a quarter to four.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.42,0:35:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许该休庭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This would probably be a suitable time for me to rise.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.33,0:35:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意明天再开始对库珀先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you content to begin your cross-examination<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.75,0:35:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行交叉讯问吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of Mr Cooper tomorrow?<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.10,0:35:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大人允许的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If My Lord would permit,<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.47,0:35:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟库珀先生谈几分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would like to have a few minutes with Mr Cooper.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.55,0:35:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好吧  伊利亚斯先生  -谢谢大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Very well, Mr Elias. - Thank you, My Lord.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.79,0:35:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库珀先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, Mr Cooper...<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:35:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你几个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would like to ask you a few questions about<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.11,0:35:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于在萨迪斯抢劫案现场附近的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the balaclava which was discovered<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.87,0:36:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灌木篱墙下发现的黑头套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}under the hedgerow near the scene of the Sardis robbery.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.45,0:36:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们  你们肯定记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ladies and gentlemen, you will remember<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.94,0:36:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这顶黑头套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that this is the balaclava which,<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.33,0:36:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是猎人行动审讯中那顶头套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the course of the Huntsman trial,<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.69,0:36:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it was found that<br />
