Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.69,0:36:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把MTJ-14证物给库珀先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could you please give Mr Cooper exhibit MTJ/14, please?<br />
