Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.42,0:36:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法医已经取完证了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The item has been cleared forensically.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.60,0:36:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触摸它不会给你造成麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Touching it won't compromise you in any way.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.32,0:36:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库珀先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr Cooper...<br />
