Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.74,0:36:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据我所知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To the best of my knowledge.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.99,0:36:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是还是不是  库珀先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes or no, Mr Cooper?<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.49,0:36:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  但萨迪斯抢劫案不是我干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. But I did not commit the Sardis robbery.<br />
