Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.14,0:36:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就从我的船上被偷走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}long before it was found under the hedgerow.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.06,0:36:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你承认那黑头套是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you accept that the balaclava is yours?<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.36,0:36:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.<br />
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.91,0:36:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库珀先生  你在1998年的猎人行动审讯中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr Cooper, that isn't what you told<br />
